{"tid":2072791,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如何用四隻字技術性擊倒白票撚？","createTime":"2020-06-21T00:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T00:48:13.000Z","uid":6518,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4dd0d6e9c23ccb9b078d4ef9586aa6b3554ce1","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:12:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>『香港獨立』</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊個候選人夠膽公開撐呢四隻字就投邊個。<br />\n<br />\n就係咁簡單。"},{"pid":"f59a4eb19716c751e127faf7eb8ec1edb4344724","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:13:31.000Z","msg":"國際戰線告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n被DQ師全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d31fdc70cec3813ae7a8d5c8a0ac61a93303d6c","tid":2072791,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:15:38.000Z","msg":"中聯辦話你知點樣 唔明顯咁封殺敏感書 (三中商）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7168fee426bb0cdeccf1e978f2f4c806d1db1a1d","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:16:18.000Z","msg":"大局為重？選你入去就係為左俾支共DQ先有國際籌碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f893d3332fd1d5dc26b1deb4286d82cd544cc2","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"獨唔獨呢啲濕鳩問題?<br />\n<br />\n唔去一次集會見識下乜野係民意主流<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港獨立，唯一出路</span></strong>"},{"pid":"28eea644a83870d6dca6aac7a2ef27c166028db6","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:33:28.000Z","msg":"告眾本土派手足<br />\n<br />\n我地只有一個任務<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">『宣揚本土意識』</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n發掘香港本土文化，從來唔係一件理性既事<br />\n<br />\n呢間黃店好難食，果個utuber啲片好長好悶<br />\n<br />\n支持本土，就係明知佢廢，你都要支持<br />\n<br />\n支持本土，本身就係一個感性既民族號召"},{"pid":"cd1d4dcd95d6c0ce2c378e402bd502534afbb2e7","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:37:54.000Z","msg":"選舉係宣揚民族意識既手段<br />\n<br />\n選你入去就係為左<strong>宣揚香港民族既獨立意識</strong><br />\n<br />\n就算被DQ你都有籌碼俾國際戰線打<br />\n<br />\n選立法會，唔單止為左含淚投票，唔單止係為左阻止保皇黨拎議席<br />\n<br />\n係為左迫支共做得更肉酸"},{"pid":"d01dc0f4c8ade3dfc5a0d0d21dfa2f3d8524ef14","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:40:45.000Z","msg":"所有行動，都係一種<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">政治宣傳</span></strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n而唔係任由白頭佬之流舒舒服服入去拎獎金"},{"pid":"173265294f63c7ca7bf602581f667563aaa5f783","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:43:12.000Z","msg":"不論你係白票撚，泛民，熱狗，本土派<br />\n<br />\n我地呢場運動只有一個共同願景<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b53a2ed76f4c88976168c194fedd28b3970fbf10","tid":2072791,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T00:48:13.000Z","msg":"選你入去唔俾人DQ仲有咩用？<br />\n<br />\n35+？ 俾假希望香港人？"}]}